```class Solution {
    public int longestDecomposition(String text) {
        int n = text.length();
        int res = 0;
        for (int i = n / 2; i > 0; i--) {
            if (text.startsWith(text.substring(i - 1)) && text.endsWith(text.substring(0, i))) {
                res = i;
                break;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
